!! Tiddler Q&A chat

Chat mode with the current tiddler's content injected as the first user message (`inject-as: user-message`, the default). The LLM can answer follow-up questions and use tools.

''Settings covered:'' chat mode, `output-mode: text`, `output-target: display`, `inject-as: user-message`, widget attribute precedence, tools enabled

```
<$llm-chat
  chatTiddler="$:/temp/rimir/llm-connect/examples/qa-chat"
  tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
  systemPrompt="You are a helpful assistant. The user will share a tiddler's content."
  tools="[tag[$:/tags/rimir/llm-connect/tool]]"
  contextTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/context-templates/default"
/>
```

